OL,3,CBusiness confidence sinks as firms
OL,4,Cweigh twin impact of US tariffs and
OL,5,Ctax rises
OL,7,FBritish business confidence slumped
OL,8,Fover the first three months of the
OL,9,Fyear, as bosses entered "a state of
OL,10,Fdespondency" over rising taxes
OL,11,Fcombined with the threat of US trade
OL,12,Ftariffs.
OL,14,FA poll by the Institute of Chartered
OL,15,FAccountants in England and Wales
OL,16,F(ICAEW) indicated that confidence is
OL,17,Fat its lowest point since late 2022,
OL,18,Fwhen inflation was surging amid the
OL,19,Fenergy crisis and Liz Truss's mini-
OL,20,FBudget.
