OL,3,CBusiness confidence sinks as firms
OL,4,Cweigh twin impact of US tariffs and
OL,5,Ctax rises
OL,7,FMore than half of companies polled in
OL,8,Fthe ICAEW's most recent survey, 56% of
OL,9,Frespondents, said taxes were a
OL,10,Fmounting challenge, an all-time high
OL,11,Ffigure.
OL,13,FAlan Vallance, the Institute's chief
OL,14,Fexecutive, said: "These findings
OL,15,Freveal a state of despondency among
OL,16,Fbusinesses as they stave off a
OL,17,Fblizzard of extra outlays, including
OL,18,Fthe rise in national insurance.
