OL,3,CBusiness confidence sinks as firms
OL,4,Cweigh twin impact of US tariffs and
OL,5,Ctax rises
OL,7,FThe ICAEW's business confidence
OL,8,Fmonitor, which produces a so-called
OL,9,Findex score from its quarterly
OL,10,Fsurveys, came in at minus 3, the
OL,11,Fweakest reading since the fourth
OL,12,Fquarter of 2022 and down from 0.2 in
OL,13,Fthe previous poll.
OL,15,FThe survey comes after weeks of
OL,16,Funcertainty over what US President
OL,17,FDonald Trump's tariffs will mean for
OL,18,FUK firms.
