OL,3,CBusiness confidence sinks as firms
OL,4,Cweigh twin impact of US tariffs and
OL,5,Ctax rises
OL,7,FAfter a chaotic few days following the
OL,8,Fannouncement of worldwide so-called
OL,9,Freciprocal import tariffs, Mr Trump
OL,10,Frolled back the measures to include a
OL,11,Fbaseline of a 10% levy for most
OL,12,Fcountries, including the UK.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, employer national insurance
OL,15,Fcontributions (Nics) rose in April at
OL,16,Fthe same time as growing utility bills
OL,17,Fand an increase in the minimum wage.
