OL,3,CBusiness confidence sinks as firms
OL,4,Cweigh twin impact of US tariffs and
OL,5,Ctax rises
OL,7,FAnd weak economic growth over recent
OL,8,Fmonths led firms to project that
OL,9,Fdomestic sales growth would hit its
OL,10,Flowest level this year since the
OL,11,Fsecond half of 2022, the ICAEW said,
OL,12,Fdespite a slight uptick in sales
OL,13,Facross those surveyed in the opening
OL,14,Fmonths of this year.
OL,16,FRecent figures from the Office for
OL,17,FNational Statistics (ONS) showed gross
OL,18,Fdomestic product (GDP) grew by 0.5% in
OL,19,FFebruary.
