OL,3,CBusiness confidence sinks as firms
OL,4,Cweigh twin impact of US tariffs and
OL,5,Ctax rises
OL,7,FBut that was a surprise leap after the
OL,8,Feconomy flatlined in January, with GDP
OL,9,Fshowing no growth in the first month
OL,10,Fof the year.
OL,12,FSuren Thiru, ICAEW economics director,
OL,13,Fadded: "These figures suggest that
OL,14,Fthis year has so far been a pretty
OL,15,Fharrowing one for the UK economy as
OL,16,Faccelerating anxiety over future sales
OL,17,Fperformance, April's eye-watering tax
OL,18,Fhike and US tariffs helped push
OL,19,Fbusiness sentiment into ominous
OL,20,Fterritory.
