OL,7,F"Our data suggests that firms are
OL,8,Fcurrently responding to intensifying
OL,9,Fcost pressures with only limited price
OL,10,Frises, but at the expense of more
OL,11,Frestrained recruitment and weaker
OL,12,Fspending on staff training, which will
OL,13,Fhinder productivity."
OL,15,FThe ONS will release its next monthly
OL,16,Freport on the UK's jobs market on
OL,17,FTuesday, while the most recent
OL,18,Finflation data is due on Wednesday.
